data.title: Dell Foundation Services
data.meta_description: I’m preparing a new Latitude E5540 running Windows 7 Pro and see Dell Foundation Services in Programs and Features. What is this program? Google did not turn up anything useful. Thanks!
data.text:
I’m preparing a new Latitude E5540 running Windows 7 Pro and see Dell Foundation Services in Programs and Features. What is this program? Google did not turn up anything useful. Thanks!

Hi iDave,

I’ve tested this out with one of our newer systems and it appears to be part of Dell Data Protection | Encryption. If you use this tool, we do not recommend removal of Dell Foundation Services.

I hope this helps!
